Johnson, E. R.; Sciegienka, J.; Carlos-Cuellar, S. and Grassian, V. H. “Heterogeneous Uptake of Gaseous Nitric Acid on Dolomite (CaMg(CO3)2) and Calcite (CaCO3) Particles: A Knudsen Cell Study Using Multiple, Single and Fractional Particle Layers” Journal of Physical Chemistry A, 2005, 109, 6901-6911.